  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effects of silymarin on outcomes of patients
      with hepatitis C.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Silymarin has been claimed to have a beneficial effect in various types of liver injury,
      including alcoholic liver disease, drug and toxin induced hepatotoxicity, and acute and
      chronic viral hepatitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
